Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.88,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.47,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたが居ればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:06.60,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,そっと横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.42,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,息を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:13.66,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,まばたきすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:17.22,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,消えてしまいそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.15,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視させて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.62,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,好きだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:30.80,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ 木々が震え 降り出した雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:38.67,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,足跡 ふたつ 白く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:45.90,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,時よ 積もれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:49.35,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,髪に 胸に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:53.02,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,二人だけの夢に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:22:00.89,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,咲けない花の種は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:06.80,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,雪に抱かれ 寄り添うの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:14.87,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに忘れられたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.88,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,我已一無所願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.47,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,只求在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:06.60,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,貼近你的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.42,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,我將呼吸消偃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:13.66,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,不肯合上眼瞼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:17.22,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,唯恐你會消散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.15,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,請勿移開視線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.62,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我傾訴愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:30.80,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚呼 枝椏微微顫 灑來殘雪翩翩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:38.67,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,足跡 相映成兩串 印下白影漣漣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:45.90,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,時光 化作積雪團團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:49.35,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,染透青絲 胭滿胸臆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:53.02,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,化作你我夢中的妝點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:22:00.89,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,花朵 遲遲不肯綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:06.80,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,唯留花種 抱雪而眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:14.87,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,在寂靜中湮滅於世間
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於還在孩童時期的我們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界充滿了驚異和威嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但等到我們長大後得到咒力後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的恐懼便會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾如此堅信著
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現場的情況推斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次戰鬥受損的比率為10：0
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鹽屋虻部落的完全勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被打敗的大黃蜂士兵們的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個都損害的很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本無法辨認出原形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個以強大軍事能力著稱的大黃蜂部落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然如此簡單的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於奇狼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從遺留品來綜合判斷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經成功撤離戰區
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但所在完全不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道跟此次的事件有沒有關聯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大黃蜂部落士兵們的遺物裡連一件兵器也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是被勝利的鹽屋虻部落的士兵拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種情況的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法使用的兵器應該扔在現場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有能稱為「武器」的武器都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 明白了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽完剛才的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位有什麼猜想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 我去現場看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據已經被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全成為了炭化狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.33,0:01:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特意去做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做了什麼見不得人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於這我有些自己的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有確鑿的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想最後提出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹽屋虻部落是不是想要掩蓋自己的攻擊手段呢？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你在那邊等我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的妖怪還真入戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn華康中圓體\pos(547,545)\c&H0334F4&\bord0\shad0}紅\N色\N的\N花
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要那條大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 幫我抓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湊成一對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 湊成一對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是妖怪來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會把它們吃掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它們放生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊 小孩子扮的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可從來沒聽過讓小孩子來扮妖怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是從今年開始的呢？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從妖鼠最近的飛速進步和軍備擴張來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們很可能是得到了某種情報源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指類蓑白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舊國會圖書館的移動式終端可能還存在數台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖鼠們可能捕獲了它們並從其獲得了知識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 瑞穗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你作為圖書管理員的見解如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有能讓大黃蜂軍團輕易全滅的手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁書…第四分類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第四分類的第三種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「殃」所記載的內容來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古代文明的確存在數種大規模的殺傷性武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過使用這些武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能瞬間消滅妖鼠的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是炸彈之類造成的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真理亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真理亞 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真理亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 剛才確實在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守…還有看不清臉的少年也在
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是前幾天實地考察時發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大黃蜂軍的箭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位有發現什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些箭上完全沒有破損的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的物品也都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遺留在戰場上大黃蜂軍的箭都是這樣的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實 假定使用了炸彈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能保存的如此完好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常攻擊時所使用的箭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是否命中目標都會留下痕跡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常的話是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按常識來考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箭上沒有痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可能是因為咒力而停留在了空中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肆星 不要緊張氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被冠上不遜的罪責
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我依然要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓大黃蜂軍全滅的是擁有咒力的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實 這樣想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與朝比奈的報告也是吻合的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說擁有咒力的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化解了大黃蜂軍所有武器的攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是相當高度的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以我們鎮為首
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有城鎮都不可能有人會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 過去從村子跑出去的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩具遺骨又作何解釋？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 所有事都變得特別可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 當時發現遺骨並向交給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這次事件的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野狐丸
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然稍費時力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是順利的話我也許還可以提供遺骨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把遺骨送回村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們應該就不會懷疑了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的骨骼在某些部分還是和神明大人的骨骼很像的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有個子高的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大小也和年輕的神明大人並無二致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一把它們的遺骨仔細打磨的話…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩具遺骨 確實是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們對其進行了嚴格的鑒定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實那是人類的骨骸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年齡 性別都與死者相一致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外還通過了DNA鑒定
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最有利的證據是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與保存在和貴園中的二人的齒形相符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋月真理亞與伊東守二人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經死亡的概率為百分之百
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 這兩人與此次事件無關
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也想和真理亞他們見上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你可能真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 早季你在來廟會之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就想到會在這裡見到他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿的浴衣與去年完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是喪服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家都會從冥界回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算看到沒什麼可奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早季你見到真理亞他們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於鹽屋虻部落及其同盟部族妖鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全會一致決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將其全部驅除 消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而關於施行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由這裡的乾帶領各位鳥獸保護官迅速執行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最後還有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於一週後的夏季祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是應該等局勢穩定下來再舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,區區妖鼠有什麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然還要把期待已久的夏季祭典也推遲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這膽小鬼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 散會
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年發生了那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來還以為廟會會延期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如期舉行真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八丁標裡怎麼會有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是乾他們回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天好像是消滅鹽屋虻部落的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有人倒下了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？難道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妖鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們肯定是知道反正會被我們殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就破釜沉舟先發動攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 這就是鹽屋虻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快通知大家
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點離開吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們打算夾擊廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對面很可能也有妖鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去廣場那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 廣場那裡…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廣場上的人們不會坐以待斃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許局勢已經有所扭轉也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為避免咒力干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請大家先把自己的咒力封印
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都交給我來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膽敢欺騙人類的惡鼠們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來拔其舌剖其屍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在太陽底下曬成肉乾如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是將其去筋碎骨疊上三層
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做成年糕呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都是從上風方向過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有毒氣 大家小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還不是蠢得一塌糊塗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上風向？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們不從能聞到我們位置的下風向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是選擇從上風向過來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然可以改變風向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邪門歪道！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為喬裝成人類就能騙過我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些鼠輩
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被區區老鼠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 如果不是我大意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何神之子的肉體是如此軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我內心的藝術就要絕跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何等浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將美之殘像…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危機暫且度過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是情況依舊不容大意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全保障會議的成員們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在的話請迅速集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後的行動按照緊急事態訓練一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請五人一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人員缺少的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迅速和其他隊伍匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能少於五人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先匯合的隊伍去巡邏小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅掉剩餘的妖鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}無論它是不是對人類忠誠的部落的還是它跪地求饒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早季
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫療相關人員請集合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把行動困難的傷員送至公民館
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳥飼小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是最愛操心最謹慎的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有宏美說過夏祭應該延期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全人學級一班只剩我們兩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和其他隊伍匯合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我十分擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己千萬要小心哦 早季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要因為擁有咒力就分散行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那惡鬼K遭遇以後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從未如此憎恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不詳的妖鼠野狐丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須要讓它受到應有的報復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓它在任何生物都沒體驗過的痛苦中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢剝奪它的生命
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋月真理亞14歲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12年前和伊東守一起逃離神棲66町
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都被確定死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡過早季
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不能讓守一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何在那小鎮無法生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且女生間是無法生小孩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑吧 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.36,0:22:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙要回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(572,411)}黑\N暗
